    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Instruments consisting of a rule that slides through a crosspiece and is inserted to measure the depth of holes, grooves, or other similar small depressions.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
